word_mean_info__list.difference: 在科学上，指单位面积上所受到的压力。用于引申时，指某事物所产生的压力或影响力等。
指某人为克服外力界压力而造成的身心和情绪等方面的压抑。用于物时，指任何力或合力作用于一个物体上面造成的应变。
侧重指承受外来的压力，也指由于某种原因而引起的心理、生理或情绪上的紧张。
多指因关系不好或其它原因而出现的紧张状态，也指某物被过度伸展的程度或状态。

bilingual.source: In spite of the case of misjudging local damage with the high order strain mode, the first order strain mode can judge and exactly indicate the location of the damage.
bilingual.target: 在高阶应变模态对结构局部损伤发生误判的情况下，一阶应变模态可以界定损伤，准确指示损伤部位。

bilingual.source: The damage factor D and the release rate of damage strain energy Y are two important parameters in Damage Mechanics.
bilingual.target: 损伤因子D和损伤应变能释放率Y是损伤力学中的两个重要参量。

bilingual.source: Don't let this be a stumbling block and strain our friendship.
bilingual.target: 别让这件事成为绊脚石，而损伤我们的友谊?釴。

bilingual.source: Strain energy change is used as damage index and a nondestructive crack detection method is proposed.
bilingual.target: 把结构遭受裂缝损伤的应变能变化量作为损伤指标，提出一种新的无损裂缝识别方法。

bilingual.source: And main types of injuries are contusion, scratch, sprain and strain.
bilingual.target: 警体运动损伤类型以挫伤 、 擦伤 、 扭伤和拉伤为主.

bilingual.source: A new four-parameter equivalent strain for isotropy damage model is presented.
bilingual.target: 提出了一种新的用于各向同性损伤模型的四参数等效应变。

bilingual.source: Finally, the stress and strain fields near the crack tip are presented.
bilingual.target: 最后得到损伤材料平面应变条件下的裂纹尖端的应力应变场。

bilingual.source: A new four - parameter equivalent strain for isotropy damage model is presented.
bilingual.target: 提出了一种新的用于各向同性损伤模型的四参数等效应变.

bilingual.source: The damage variable is defined as the residual strain of concrete under constant amplitude fatigue loading, and the law of cumulative damage and its evolution are obtained.
bilingual.target: 由等幅疲劳残余应变，定义了损伤变量，得到了相应的损伤积累和演化规律。

bilingual.source: Another emphasis of this paper is the research on damage evolvement of SFRHSC and foundation of strain rate sensitive constitutive relation containing damage.
bilingual.target: 本文的另一重点是研究钢纤维高强混凝土的损伤演化、建立含损伤的率型本构模型。

yingyinNormal.en: Could be pneumococcal. Most likely an aggressive flu strain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能是肺炎球菌，很可能是一种急性流感。

yingyinNormal.en: I've already developed a virus strain that I think will be more aggressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经研发出一个病种我认为会更有效。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: Your body will strain to reject the poison by profusely sweating, defecating, vomiting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 免疫系统会尽其所能排除毒素，大量出汗，上吐下泻。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I can appreciate that. Gas prices right now are putting a strain on everybody's pocketbooks. Isn't that true?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我理解拼车的各位，这年头的油价快把大家都烧穷了。你们说对不对？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: For example, a high growth rate placed great <highlight>strains</highlight> on the existing structures of governance, of administration, and above all of socialization.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，高增长率给现有的治理结构、行政结构、尤其是社会化结构带来了巨大压力。

examination_example.sentence: It must rely on low-wage overseas labor, order in volumes that <highlight>strain</highlight> natural resources, and use massive amounts of harmful chemicals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它必须依靠廉价的海外劳动力，大批量订货以致过度消耗自然资源，还有使用大量的有害化学物质。

sense_info_list.en: an injury to a part of the body caused by overexertion or twisting
a particular breed of an animal or plant
a force tending to pull or stretch something to an extreme or damaging degree

word_usage.usage:
strain作动词，表示“过度使用”时，为及物动词，可直接跟名词。例：
Increases in oil prices have strained the company's finances.
油料价格的上涨让公司财务支出过多。

examination_example.sentence: Over the next year and a half investigators will test the various <highlight>strains</highlight> of saline-tolerant rice they've concocted.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在接下来的一年半时间里，调查员将测试他们培育出的各种耐盐水稻。

examination_example.sentence: The problem has grown into such epidemic proportions that this severe <highlight>strain</highlight> of resistant bacteria is being blamed for nearly 700, 000 deaths each year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个问题已经发展到如此流行的程度，以至于每年有近70万人因这种严重的耐药细菌而死亡。

examination_example.sentence: Vital local services including waste collection, park maintenance and arts and culture spending are under unprecedented <highlight>strain</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 包括废物收集、公园维护和艺术文化支出在内的重要地方服务都面临着前所未有的压力。

examination_example.sentence: Turning every single word into the target language would put too much <highlight>strain</highlight> on the interpreter and slow down the whole process too much.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 将每个单词都翻译成目标语言会给翻译人员带来很大的压力，并大大降低整个过程的速度。
